The paper discusses the application of deep learning techniques to address challenges in recommender systems, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms to improve the accuracy and efficiency of recommender systems, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing techniques to improve recommender systems, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of deep learning techniques for image and audio processing, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV).
